layout.text: The A Ma Maniére Air Jordan 1 is the latest sneaker collaboration with Jordan Brand, building on the tradition of classic, timeless luxury that anchors the A Ma Maniére brand. Featuring a fine cracked leather upper, snakeskin details and a quilted liner and collar now synonymous with the joining of the minds between A Ma Maniére and Jordan Brand design, this Air Jordan 1 is a piece to be celebrated and cherished for its special details and luxurious execution.
